# =============================================================================
# LAPLACE Client Distribution — SERVER-ONLY files
# =============================================================================
#
# This manifest lists files that MUST NOT be included in any client-facing
# distribution (.exe installer, cloud desktop setup, ZIP bundle, etc.).
#
# These files contain the sensitive IP (scoring formulas, betting sequences,
# threshold constants, regularity algorithms) that make the LAPLACE strategy
# valuable. They must live only on the VPS, where the LAPLACE API serves
# decisions to clients over HTTP.
#
# When building a client distribution, filter out every path listed below.
# When running the client, these files are lazily imported only in
# local-fallback mode (which should be disabled in shipped builds via
# LAPLACE_USE_REMOTE=1).
#
# Format: one glob pattern per line. Lines starting with '#' are comments.
# =============================================================================

# --- Core strategy logic (highest sensitivity) ---
marubatsu_strategy.py
marubatsu_bet.py
run_marubatsu_bet.py

# --- Table selection and scoring ---
table_selector.py

# --- Regularity and shoe pattern analysis ---
shoe.py
strategy.py

